      "writtenOn": "2016-11-23T20:54:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Fair enough, but if \u0027myval\u0027 is also a valid index value, then when I do an index lookup for \u0027myval\u0027 then I will also get results for \u0027myvalX\u0027, with results that are prefixed with an extra X.",
      "parentUuid": "4df48341_e2b7681f",
      "revId": "934d452274e35e40ffc77e3ba16e9b5616afbc99",
